5: Oh, here he comes. Hi, Aureo!
9:
Good morning! Hope you weren't 
waiting too long.
11:
Here are the lunch boxes you ordered. 
They're enchanted, so they'll still be 
warm when you open 'em!
23: How deep are you headed today?
27:
The midways. There's an unexplored 
section we have our eyes on.
30:
The midways?! Ooh, I wish I could go 
too!
34: You wanna come with us, then?
41:
The unexplored regions can be pretty 
dangerous, though. A porter would just 
be extra baggage.
45:
Hey, c'mon. You're still sayin' stuff like 
that?
48:
Yeah, you and Baloosh are always 
welcome to tag along! An extra pair of 
hands in the Kaleidoscope never hurts.
52:
Thanks! I can't wait!
Oh, but... um...
55:
You've got other deliveries scheduled? 
Don't worry, we're going in again 
tomorrow. Just meet us here in the 
morning!
63:
Oh! Over here! Good morning, you 
two.
78:
S-sorry, I'm fine! Just didn't get much 
sleep.
80:
I was having so much fun planning 
everything for today, I lost track of the 
time...
84:
Fatigue dulls your senses—we should 
reschedule to another day.
88:
What?! No way! I'm fine, really! Please 
let me go with you, pleeeease!
92:
I dunno, I'm kinda with Light. The 
Kaleidoscope isn't going anywhere.
101:
Hmm. I believe Baloosh is trying to say, 
"leave Aureo to me."
105:
Huh? Wait, you could understand 
that?
107:
No, I just get the feeling Baloosh is 
excited to explore the Kaleidoscope 
with him.
112:
Yeah, they WERE both looking forward 
to this a lot, huh...
All right, you two can come.
126: The sun's already starting to set.
130:
Whew! My heart was pounding the 
whole time!
134:
You did well, Aureo. I wouldn't have 
guessed this was your first time in the 
midways.
138:
Hehe, thanks! But it was Baloosh who 
did all the hard work!
142:
Baloosh has a very good eye for 
spotting treasure and monsters.
147:
Yup! I dunno what I'd do without 
Baloosh at my side!
151: You two certainly are good friends.
160:
We don't know what kind of bird 
Baloosh is, but someday when I've 
saved up enough, I want to go on 
a quest to find out.
164:
Make sure you invite us when you do! 
We'd love to help.
177:
You look pretty sleepy yourself. 
You two had a big day.
181:
I'm fine. I'll stay here and wait for 
Baloosh to wake up.
182:
Usually Baloosh is the one looking over 
me when I fall asleep, so I've gotta take 
my chance to return to the favor.
194:
I suppose we could babysit them for 
a quick nap before sending them 
home.
